high_descs: Turn to your left and head towards the counters, then turn right and head towards the counters.
Pick up the knife.
Turn around and head towards the blue recycle bin.
Cut the tomato that is in the bin.
Put the knife in the bin.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn to the right and face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the slice in the fridge, close the door, wait a bit, open the door and take the slice out of the fridge.
Turn to the right of the fridge, walk a bit and then and face the microwave.
Place the slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: place a slice of tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Move to the counter top to the left of the stove
Pick up the knife on top of the counter to the left of the stove
Carry the knife to the blue recycling bin
Cut the potato in the recycling bin
Place the knife in the blue recycling bin
Pick up a slice of the potato
Carry the potato slice to the fridge
Open the fridge, place slice of potato in fridge, close, then remove potato
Carry the potato slice to the microwave
Place the potato slice inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato slice from the recycling where the knife was recycled

high_descs: turn left and walk to the dishwasher at the end of the room, then turn right and walk over to the stove
grab the butter knife off of the kitchen counter to the left of the stove
turn right and walk to the kitchen counter ahead, then take a right and walk over to the blue recycling bin on the floor to the left of the fridge ahead
cut up the potato inside of the recycling bin
place the butter knife down inside the recycling bin
grab the potato slice out of the recycling bin
look up and move to the right a bit so that you're facing the center of the fridge
place the potato slice inside of the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
move to the right a bit and face the microwave on the kitchen counter to your left
place the potato slice inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a cooled potato slice inside of the microwave

high_descs: Turn left, head to the counter, then turn right and head to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife.
Turn around and head to the blue bin on the left of the fridge.
Cut the tomato.
Put the knife in the bin.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn and head to the fridge and face the fridge.
Open the door, place the slice of tomato in, close the door, wait a bit, open the door, take out the slice and close the door.
Turn and walk to the left, then face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the slice in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of tomato in the fridge for a bit before putting it in the microwave.
